This is due to ActivitiesManager#serviceStop interrupt the thread and come out. But exception handling in run method ignores exception and continue in loop.
{code}
    cleanUpThread = new Thread(new Runnable() {
      @Override
      public void run() {
        while (true) {
          // some code
          try {
            Thread.sleep(5000);
          } catch (Exception e) {
            // ignore
          }
        }
      }
    });
{code}
